author: Journal Inquirer Staff
title: Somers gets clutch goal from Kwasnik
text:
JIM MICHAUD Bolton-Stafford Soccer 
Stafford 12, Sarah Gallison, and Bolton 12, Julie Hinkley, in the first half of the game,   2015, at Bolton High School. (Jim Michaud   Wednesday, October 21, 2015 10:02 am | Updated: 10:04 am, Wed Oct 21, 2015. 
After a scoreless first half, the Somers and East Windsor girls soccer teams went on the offensive during the first nine minutes of the second half Tuesday. 
When the barrage was over, the Spartans had an edge they would not relinquish.
